><A HREF="gc.htm"> Of God and His Creatures</a><hr><p>
Abu Hamed Mohammed Algazali, A.D. 1058-1111, a theologian of the 
orthodox Mohammedan school, wrote a work <i>Destructions of 
Philosophers</i>, to which Averroes replied with <i>Destruction of 
Destructions</i>. Algazali denied the eternity of the world. 

